  description: Increases Armor by 5 and Critical Strike Chance by 20%. Every 5th
    time the wearer takes damage, they release a burst of fire dealing Magic Damage
    to all adjacent enemies. The wearer's next basic attack after the burst is a
    guaranteed Critical Strike. Heavy plate gauntlets that glow with a dull, infernal
    red, smelling faintly of sulfur and scorched iron.
